<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <title>sharedearth.net</title>
  <%= render :partial => "layouts/meta_header" %>
  <style>
		html {
			background: url('/static/graphics/bg-html.png') repeat-x 0 0 ;
		}
		body {
			padding:20px;
			background-color:Transparent;
		}
		input, button { padding:2px; }
  </style>
</head>

<body>
	<p>
	In future different sign-in methods will be included, so humans without Facebook accounts can connect to sharedearth.net.
	</p>
	<br />
	<p>
	To be informed when this happens, leave your email address below, and respond to the confirmation email.
	</p>
	<br />
	<form action="http://groups.google.com/group/sharedearthnet/boxsubscribe" target="_blank" onsubmit="setTimeout(function(){this.close();},0)">
		<div>
			<input style="width:250px;" onfocus="this.value=''" type="text" value="Email" name="email" />
			<input type="submit" value="Connect" />
		</div>
	</form>
</body>
</html>

